RAW_96CN: com/fs/starfarer/launcher/opengl/GLModPickerV2.setSelected - String - "该 MOD 与前置 MOD 版本不符。"

LDC_96CN: "该 MOD 与前置 MOD 版本不符。但仍可运行。"
RAW_96CN: com/fs/starfarer/launcher/opengl/GLModPickerV2.setSelected - String - "该 MOD 与前置 MOD 版本不符。但仍可运行。"

LDC: "Warning: this mod requires a different version of a mod that you have installed, but might run with this one."
LDC_96CN: "警告: 这个 mod 需要的前置 mod 版本号和您已经安装前置 mod 版本不同，但或许也可以正常运行"
RAW_96CN: com/fs/starfarer/launcher/opengl/GLModPickerV2.setSelected - String - "警告: 这个 mod 需要的前置 mod 版本号和您已经安装前置 mod 版本不同，但或许也可以正常运行"

LDC_96CN: "需要实弹、能量或混合武器槽"
RAW_96CN: com/fs/starfarer/ui/impl/CargoTooltipFactory.o00000 - String - "需要实弹、能量或混合武器槽"

LDC: "Requires an Energy, Missile, or Synergy slot"
LDC_96CN: "需要能量、导弹或协同武器槽"
RAW_96CN: com/fs/starfarer/ui/impl/CargoTooltipFactory.o00000 - String - "需要能量、导弹或协同武器槽"

LDC: "Requires a Ballistic, Missile, or Composite slot"
LDC_96CN: "需要实弹、导弹或复合武器槽"
RAW_96CN: com/fs/starfarer/ui/impl/CargoTooltipFactory.o00000 - String - "需要实弹、导弹或复合武器槽"

LDC: "Can be installed in any type of slot"
LDC_96CN: "可安装在任何类型的武器槽中"
RAW_96CN: com/fs/starfarer/ui/impl/CargoTooltipFactory.o00000 - String - "可安装在任何类型的武器槽中"

LDC_96CN: "幅能 / 非 EMP 伤害 (比率) "
RAW_96CN: com/fs/starfarer/ui/impl/CargoTooltipFactory.o00000 - String - "幅能 / 非 EMP 伤害 (比率) "

LDC: "Seeing remote price data for various colonies requires being within range of a functional comm relay."
LDC_96CN: "必须在功能强大的通信中继器范围内，才可查看各个殖民地的远程价格数据。"
RAW_96CN: com/fs/starfarer/ui/impl/CargoTooltipFactory.o00000 - String - "必须在功能强大的通信中继器范围内，才可查看各个殖民地的远程价格数据。"

LDC: "All values approximate. Prices do not include tariffs, which can be avoided through black market trade."
LDC_96CN: "所有价格的大概值。不包括关税，而关税可通过黑市交易来避免。"
RAW_96CN: com/fs/starfarer/ui/impl/CargoTooltipFactory.o00000 - String - "所有价格的大概值。不包括关税，而关税可通过黑市交易来避免。"

LDC: "*Per unit prices assume buying or selling a batch of %s units. Each unit bought costs more as the market's supply is reduced, and each unit sold brings in less as demand is fulfilled."
LDC_96CN: "假设每一批的买入或卖出为 %s 单位，随着市场供应量的降低，每单位买入的成本将随之提高，而随着需求得到满足，每单位卖出的价格也将降低。"
RAW_96CN: com/fs/starfarer/ui/impl/CargoTooltipFactory.o00000 - String - "假设每一批的买入或卖出为 %s 单位，随着市场供应量的降低，每单位买入的成本将随之提高，而随着需求得到满足，每单位卖出的价格也将降低。"
com/fs/starfarer/campaign/accidents/O0OO.super - String - " 遭遇灾难性的失败"

LDC: "Dispose of excess fuel, or acquire more ships to increase you fleet's fuel capacity"
LDC_96CN: "处理掉多余的燃料，或提高更多的船只去提高你的舰队的燃料容量"
RAW_96CN: com/fs/starfarer/campaign/accidents/O0OO.String - String - "处理掉多余的燃料，或提高更多的船只去提高你的舰队的燃料容量"

LDC: "Your flagship for this tutorial is a Hammerhead class destroyer. First things first - let's learn how to get it moving."
LDC_96CN: "本教程中你的旗舰是一艘锤头-级驱逐舰。我们先来学习舰船操作中最基本的 - 移动。"
RAW_96CN: com/fs/starfarer/tutorial/A.createScript - String - "本教程中你的旗舰是一艘锤头-级驱逐舰。我们先来学习舰船操作中最基本的 - 移动。"

LDC: "(By the way - you can pause and unpause the game at any time by pressing "
RAW_96CN: com/fs/starfarer/tutorial/A.createScript - String - " (顺便说一句 - 你可以按 "

LDC_96CN: " 来在任何时候暂停游戏。) "
RAW_96CN: com/fs/starfarer/tutorial/A.createScript - String - " 来在任何时候暂停游戏。) "

LDC: "Press %s and %s to turn, %s and %s to accelerate forward or back, and hold %s to bring your ship to a halt. Give this a try, and press "Continue" when you've got the hang of it."
LDC_96CN: "按键盘 %s 和 %s 旋转转向，%s 和 %s 加速或反方向加速，和按 %s 把船停下来。您可以试操作一下，熟悉了后就点 "继续"."
RAW_96CN: com/fs/starfarer/tutorial/A.createScript - String - "按键盘 %s 和 %s 旋转转向，%s 和 %s 加速或反方向加速，和按 %s 把船停下来。您可以试操作一下，熟悉了后就点 "继续"."

LDC: "Moving the mouse around pans your view. You can also use the mouse wheel to zoom in and out."
LDC_96CN: "以鼠标左右移动改变视野位置，滚轮缩放视野。"
RAW_96CN: com/fs/starfarer/tutorial/A.createScript - String - "以鼠标左右移动改变视野位置，滚轮缩放视野。"

LDC: "Your ship will turn towards your mouse pointer while you strafe, so keep the cursor on top of the target."
LDC_96CN: "如果您在移动时想用舰首武器扫射敌舰，请把光标对准目标。"
RAW_96CN: com/fs/starfarer/tutorial/A.createScript - String - "如果您在移动时想用舰首武器扫射敌舰，请把光标对准目标。"

LDC: "There's now an enemy ship - an Enforcer-class destroyer - at your 12 o'clock. Its weapon and maneuvering systems are disabled."
LDC_96CN: "现在系统为您生成了一艘虚拟敌舰，它是一艘执法者-级驱逐舰，就在您 12 点方向。别担心，它的动力和武装系统均已下线。"
RAW_96CN: com/fs/starfarer/tutorial/A.createScript - String - "现在系统为您生成了一艘虚拟敌舰，它是一艘执法者-级驱逐舰，就在您 12 点方向。别担心，它的动力和武装系统均已下线。"

LDC: "Guided missiles require a target. By default, they'll lock on to the enemy nearest to your cursor when you fire."
LDC_96CN: "制导导弹会自动锁定一个目标。如果您不去为它们选目标的话，它们会自动锁定开火时离光标最近的敌人。"
RAW_96CN: com/fs/starfarer/tutorial/A.createScript - String - "制导导弹会自动锁定一个目标。如果您不去为它们选目标的话，它们会自动锁定开火时离光标最近的敌人。"

LDC: "You can also lock onto a specific enemy to ensure missiles go after it, and to see more information about it."
LDC_96CN: "你还可以锁定一个特定的敌人，以确保导弹去追击它，同时，您也能查看锁定目标的详细信息。"
RAW_96CN: com/fs/starfarer/tutorial/A.createScript - String - "你还可以锁定一个特定的敌人，以确保导弹去追击它，同时，您也能查看锁定目标的详细信息。"

LDC: "Hover over the enemy ship and press %s to target it."
LDC_96CN: "将光标停留在敌舰上并按 %s 就可以锁定它。"
RAW_96CN: com/fs/starfarer/tutorial/A.createScript - String - "将光标停留在敌舰上并按 %s 就可以锁定它。"

LDC: "Firing most weapons (except for missiles) generates flux. Your ship has a limited flux capacity, and managing what you use it on is key to survival. You can see your current flux level on the info display in the lower left corner of the screen."
LDC_96CN: "大多数武器 (除了导弹) 开火都会产生幅能。而舰船的幅能容量是有上限的，所以对幅能合适的管理决定了您在战场上的表现...以及性命。您可在屏幕左下角的舰船信息上悉知你目前的幅能容量。"
RAW_96CN: com/fs/starfarer/tutorial/A.createScript - String - "大多数武器 (除了导弹) 开火都会产生幅能。而舰船的幅能容量是有上限的，所以对幅能合适的管理决定了您在战场上的表现...以及性命。您可在屏幕左下角的舰船信息上悉知你目前的幅能容量。"
com/fs/starfarer/tutorial/A.createScript - String - "辐能|幅能容量|管理"

LDC: "Fire your Assault Chainguns (group 1) for a bit and watch how they build up flux, then continue when you're ready."
LDC_96CN: "您可以试着用您的突击链炮 (1 号武器组) 发射几枚子弹，并仔细观察下它们是怎么产生幅能的，了解后点继续。"
RAW_96CN: com/fs/starfarer/tutorial/A.createScript - String - "您可以试着用您的突击链炮 (1 号武器组) 发射几枚子弹，并仔细观察下它们是怎么产生幅能的，了解后点继续。"

LDC: "The flux from firing these dissipates almost as quickly as it's generated. Different ships and ship loadouts dissipate flux at different rates, and so can support varying amounts of weapons effectively."
LDC_96CN: "射击产生的幅能会很快耗散，但不同舰船的幅能耗散速度是不同的，所以携带的武器也多种多样。"
RAW_96CN: com/fs/starfarer/tutorial/A.createScript - String - "射击产生的幅能会很快耗散，但不同舰船的幅能耗散速度是不同的，所以携带的武器也多种多样。"

LDC: "Shields generate flux continuously while they're up, and generate even more flux every time they absorb damage."
LDC_96CN: "护盾只要一开启就会持续产生幅能，不仅如此，在吸收伤害时将会产生更多幅能。"
RAW_96CN: com/fs/starfarer/tutorial/A.createScript - String - "护盾只要一开启就会持续产生幅能，不仅如此，在吸收伤害时将会产生更多幅能。"

LDC: "(So, even if you're not taking any damage on the shields, keeping them off will let you put out more firepower.)"
LDC_96CN: " (所以，在你未受到过多威胁时，保持护盾的关闭可以让你释放出更强大的火力。) "
RAW_96CN: com/fs/starfarer/tutorial/A.createScript - String - " (所以，在你未受到过多威胁时，保持护盾的关闭可以让你释放出更强大的火力。) "

LDC: "Now, let's see how the shields hold up under fire."
LDC_96CN: "现在，让我们看看护盾是怎样承受炮火的。"
RAW_96CN: com/fs/starfarer/tutorial/A.createScript - String - "现在，让我们看看护盾是怎样承受炮火的。"

LDC: "The enemy ship has stopped firing, but your flux level still isn't going down!"
LDC_96CN: "看到了吧，尽管敌舰已停止射击，但是您的幅能水平仍居高不下。"
RAW_96CN: com/fs/starfarer/tutorial/A.createScript - String - "看到了吧，尽管敌舰已停止射击，但是您的幅能水平仍居高不下。"

LDC: "Flux gained when shields absorb damage is called hard flux and only dissipates while the shields are off - so, you can't keep shields up indefinitely while taking damage."
LDC_96CN: "护盾吸收伤害时产生的幅能是 '硬' 幅能，它只能在护盾关闭时才可耗散。所以一直挂着护盾妄想半无敌的梦就别做了。"
RAW_96CN: com/fs/starfarer/tutorial/A.createScript - String - "护盾吸收伤害时产生的幅能是 '硬' 幅能，它只能在护盾关闭时才可耗散。所以一直挂着护盾妄想半无敌的梦就别做了。"

LDC: "Flux gained from firing weapons is called soft flux, and can dissipate while the shields are up."
LDC_96CN: "武器开火时产生的幅能是 '软' 幅能，而它能在护盾开启时耗散。"
RAW_96CN: com/fs/starfarer/tutorial/A.createScript - String - "武器开火时产生的幅能是 '软' 幅能，而它能在护盾开启时耗散。"

LDC: "The notch on the flux bar indicates your hard flux level."
LDC_96CN: "幅能条上的凸起代表了您当前的硬幅能水平。"
RAW_96CN: com/fs/starfarer/tutorial/A.createScript - String - "幅能条上的凸起代表了您当前的硬幅能水平。"

LDC: " to turn off your shields and let the flux dissipate."
LDC_96CN: " 关掉你的护盾让幅能耗散。"
RAW_96CN: com/fs/starfarer/tutorial/A.createScript - String - " 关掉你的护盾让幅能耗散。"

LDC: "Good. Now, let's see what happens if you keep your shields on under fire for too long."
LDC_96CN: "好。现在，让我们看看如果你保持护盾在对面火力下太久会发生什么。"
RAW_96CN: com/fs/starfarer/tutorial/A.createScript - String - "好。现在，让我们看看如果你保持护盾在对面火力下太久会发生什么。"

LDC: "%s to turn on your shields again and let the enemy keep firing at you."
LDC_96CN: "%s 再次打开你的护盾，让敌人不断向你射击。"
RAW_96CN: com/fs/starfarer/tutorial/A.createScript - String - "%s 再次打开你的护盾，让敌人不断向你射击。"

LDC: "As you can see, it's not good - when flux maxes out from shield hits, your ship overloads."
LDC_96CN: "如您所见，当护盾吸收的伤害使幅能超过上限后，您的舰船将直接过载并关闭护盾。"
RAW_96CN: com/fs/starfarer/tutorial/A.createScript - String - "如您所见，当护盾吸收的伤害使幅能超过上限后，您的舰船将直接过载并关闭护盾。"

LDC: "While the ship is overloaded, it can't fire or raise shields, dissipates flux very slowly, but can still maneuver normally."
LDC_96CN: "当舰船过载时，就无法射击或使用护盾了，而且只会以非常缓慢的速度耗散幅能，幸运的是，您仍然能控制其移动 (在脆弱的引擎还没被打爆的前提下) "
RAW_96CN: com/fs/starfarer/tutorial/A.createScript - String - "当舰船过载时，就无法射击或使用护盾了，而且只会以非常缓慢的速度耗散幅能，幸运的是，您仍然能控制其移动 (在脆弱的引擎还没被打爆的前提下) "

LDC: "Now that the ship is no longer overloaded, flux is back to dissipating at a normal rate."
LDC_96CN: "好了，现在舰船已经不再过载了，幅能耗散也恢复到正常水平。"
RAW_96CN: com/fs/starfarer/tutorial/A.createScript - String - "好了，现在舰船已经不再过载了，幅能耗散也恢复到正常水平。"

LDC: "You can also vent flux to dissipate it at double the normal rate."
LDC_96CN: "您也可以主动排幅，以正常两倍的耗散速率来迅速排放幅能。"
RAW_96CN: com/fs/starfarer/tutorial/A.createScript - String - "您也可以主动排幅，以正常两倍的耗散速率来迅速排放幅能。"

LDC: "While venting, your ship can't fire or use shields, so you generally only want to do it when it's safe."
LDC_96CN: "当您在主动排幅时，您的舰船是不能使用武器或护盾的，所以一般只有在安全情况下才会启用。且无法取消，只能等到结束。"
RAW_96CN: com/fs/starfarer/tutorial/A.createScript - String - "当您在主动排幅时，您的舰船是不能使用武器或护盾的，所以一般只有在安全情况下才会启用。且无法取消，只能等到结束。"

LDC_96CN: "那么现在按 %s 键来主动排幅。"
RAW_96CN: com/fs/starfarer/tutorial/A.createScript - String - "那么现在按 %s 键来主动排幅。"

LDC: "Good. As you can see, you've now been flanked by a pair of Lasher-class frigates."
LDC_96CN: "您看！您正被两艘征伐-级护卫舰夹击。"
RAW_96CN: com/fs/starfarer/tutorial/A.createScript - String - "您看！您正被两艘征伐-级护卫舰夹击。"

LDC: "They're going to start launching missiles at you. Fortunately, these missiles aren't very effective vs well-armored ships."
LDC_96CN: "他们正在向您发射导弹。还好，这些导弹对您那精良的装甲没有多大效果。"
RAW_96CN: com/fs/starfarer/tutorial/A.createScript - String - "他们正在向您发射导弹。还好，这些导弹对您那精良的装甲没有多大效果。"

LDC: "Just sit tight and let them get a few volleys off."
LDC_96CN: "您大可以坐下来喝杯茶等它们几轮齐射完毕。"
RAW_96CN: com/fs/starfarer/tutorial/A.createScript - String - "您大可以坐下来喝杯茶等它们几轮齐射完毕。"

LDC: "It'd be nice to shoot these down - we've got some point-defense lasers just for that. But, it's almost impossible to manually target all the incoming missiles."
LDC_96CN: "能拦截那些导弹就好了 - 而我们正好有防御激光。但是，要手动瞄准拦截那些导弹几乎是不可能的。"
RAW_96CN: com/fs/starfarer/tutorial/A.createScript - String - "能拦截那些导弹就好了 - 而我们正好有防御激光。但是，要手动瞄准拦截那些导弹几乎是不可能的。"

LDC: "Fortunately, you can set any weapon group on autofire, making the weapons identify and attack targets on their own."
LDC_96CN: "幸运的是，还好您可以将任何武器组，设置成自动开火模式。"
RAW_96CN: com/fs/starfarer/tutorial/A.createScript - String - "幸运的是，还好您可以将任何武器组，设置成自动开火模式。"

LDC: "Press %s to enable autofire for the point-defense lasers in group 3. Make sure you have a different group selected - selecting an autofiring group will result in a manual override of its controls."
LDC_96CN: "按下 %s 让位于编组 3 的点防御激光进入自动开火模式，然后确保你选定了另一个武器编组。自动开火模式编组被选定时将强制进入手动控制模式。"
RAW_96CN: com/fs/starfarer/tutorial/A.createScript - String - "按下 %s 让位于编组 3 的点防御激光进入自动开火模式，然后确保你选定了另一个武器编组。自动开火模式编组被选定时将强制进入手动控制模式。"

LDC: "Note how the lasers switch to attacking the missiles as soon as they're launched - point defense weapons will prioritize targeting missiles."
LDC_96CN: "因为这些激光是点防御系统，所以它们会优先攻击制导导弹。"
RAW_96CN: com/fs/starfarer/tutorial/A.createScript - String - "因为这些激光是点防御系统，所以它们会优先攻击制导导弹。"

LDC: "Regular weapons will not target missiles automatically."
LDC_96CN: "但要注意，常规武器通常是不会自动瞄准导弹的。"
RAW_96CN: com/fs/starfarer/tutorial/A.createScript - String - "但要注意，常规武器通常是不会自动瞄准导弹的。"

LDC: "Each ship also has a special system - an active ability it can perform. For the Hammerhead, it's an Accelerated Ammo Feeder that greatly increases the rate of fire for ballistic weapons."
LDC_96CN: "每艘舰船都有一个自己独特的能力。比如这艘锤头-级，它的加速填弹器可以极大得提升弹道武器的射速。"
RAW_96CN: com/fs/starfarer/tutorial/A.createScript - String - "每艘舰船都有一个自己独特的能力。比如这艘锤头-级，它的加速填弹器可以极大得提升弹道武器的射速。"

LDC: "Some ship systems have limited uses, some generate flux, some have a cooldown - and some use a combination of those."
LDC_96CN: "有些舰船的系统使用次数有限，有些会产生幅能，而且需要冷却。"
RAW_96CN: com/fs/starfarer/tutorial/A.createScript - String - "有些舰船的系统使用次数有限，有些会产生幅能，而且需要冷却。"

LDC: "The Accelerated Ammo Feeder must cool down before it can be used again."
LDC_96CN: "而加速填弹器必须冷却完毕才能再次使用。"
RAW_96CN: com/fs/starfarer/tutorial/A.createScript - String - "而加速填弹器必须冷却完毕才能再次使用。"

LDC: "Press %s to activate the Accelerated Ammo Feeder and fire the Assault Chainguns (group 1) to see its effect."
LDC_96CN: "您可以按 %s 激活加速填弹器，并用突击链炮开火看看它的效果吧。"

RAW_96CN: com/fs/starfarer/coreui/refit/Object$3.createImpl - String - "开启护盾时所收到的伤害会转换成 "硬" 幅能，只有关闭护盾才可耗散。"

LDC: "Flux is dissipated at double the normal rate while actively venting."
LDC_96CN: "主动排幅的速率一般是正常幅能耗散的两倍。"
RAW_96CN: com/fs/starfarer/coreui/refit/Object$3.createImpl - String - "主动排幅的速率一般是正常幅能耗散的两倍。"

LDC: "Each vent costs %s ordnance point and increases dissipation by %s flux per second."
LDC_96CN: "每提高 %s 点耗散通道，就额外获得 %s 点幅能耗散。"
RAW_96CN: com/fs/starfarer/coreui/refit/Object$4.createImpl - String - "每提高 %s 点耗散通道，就额外获得 %s 点幅能耗散。"

LDC: "Firing weapons and using shields generates flux."
LDC_96CN: "武器开火与开启护盾都将会产生软幅能。"
RAW_96CN: com/fs/starfarer/coreui/refit/Object$2.createImpl - String - "武器开火与开启护盾都将会产生软幅能。"

LDC: "A ship with a high flux capacity is able to absorb more damage with shields and pour out more weapons fire during a window of opportunity, increasing its short-term effectiveness."
LDC_96CN: "一艘具有高幅能容量的战舰都能用护盾承受大量伤害并予以猛烈还击。"
RAW_96CN: com/fs/starfarer/coreui/refit/Object$2.createImpl - String - "一艘具有高幅能容量的战舰都能用护盾承受大量伤害并予以猛烈还击。"

LDC: "It may also be more vulnerable while waiting for the built-up flux to dissipate, especially since higher flux capacity often comes at the expense of the dissipation rate."
LDC_96CN: "当累计的幅能逐渐接近上限，本舰的作战能力也将大幅下降，尤其是 那些以牺牲幅能耗散来提升幅能容量的舰船。"
RAW_96CN: com/fs/starfarer/coreui/refit/Object$2.createImpl - String - "当累计的幅能逐渐接近上限，本舰的作战能力也将大幅下降，尤其是 那些以牺牲幅能耗散来提升幅能容量的舰船。"

LDC: "Damage that gets through armor and shields gets applied to the hull. Taking hull damage can cause weapons and engines to become temporarily disabled, and is likely to result in casualties among the crew."
LDC_96CN: "越过装甲与护盾的伤害会直接影响到船体结构，而船体受损会导致武器 引擎暂时失效，也可导致船员伤亡。"
RAW_96CN: com/fs/starfarer/coreui/refit/Object$7.createImpl - String - "越过装甲与护盾的伤害会直接影响到船体结构，而船体受损会导致武器 引擎暂时失效，也可导致船员伤亡。"

LDC: "Once hull reaches zero, the ship becomes disabled, though it may be recoverable (by the winner) after the battle ends."
LDC_96CN: "一旦船体结构为零，舰船就会彻底失去作用，尽管它可能在战斗结束后 (胜利后) 恢复。"
RAW_96CN: com/fs/starfarer/coreui/refit/Object$7.createImpl - String - "一旦船体结构为零，舰船就会彻底失去作用，尽管它可能在战斗结束后 (胜利后) 恢复。"

LDC: "Armor reduces the damage taken by a percentage that depends on the relative strength of the armor compared to the amount of damage, and blocks damage from getting through to the hull."
LDC_96CN: "装甲可以降低一定百分比的伤害，也能阻止伤害直接穿透至结构当中，其效果取决于装甲与所承受伤害的强度。"
RAW_96CN: com/fs/starfarer/coreui/refit/Object$8.createImpl - String - "装甲可以降低一定百分比的伤害，也能阻止伤害直接穿透至结构当中，其效果取决于装甲与所承受伤害的强度。"

LDC: "Each hit reduces the amount of armor that remains in the affected area, making each successive hit more and more powerful."
LDC_96CN: "每次攻击都会降低受影响区域的装甲强度，如果同区域承受多次伤害，其对船体结构造成的损伤也将越来越大。"
RAW_96CN: com/fs/starfarer/coreui/refit/Object$8.createImpl - String - "每次攻击都会降低受影响区域的装甲强度，如果同区域承受多次伤害，其对船体结构造成的损伤也将越来越大。"

LDC: "Damage applied in a single hit is much more effective at stripping away armor than the same damage distributed over multiple hits."
LDC_96CN: "一次攻击中造成的伤害比在多次攻击中造成的相同伤害更有效。"
RAW_96CN: com/fs/starfarer/coreui/refit/Object$8.createImpl - String - "一次攻击中造成的伤害比在多次攻击中造成的相同伤害更有效。"

LDC: "The "hit strength" of beam weapons - which do not score separate hits, but deal damage continuously - is based on their damage/second."
LDC_96CN: "光束武器无需连续攻击就可持续造成伤害，其破坏力取决于 伤害/秒。"
RAW_96CN: com/fs/starfarer/coreui/refit/Object$8.createImpl - String - "光束武器无需连续攻击就可持续造成伤害，其破坏力取决于 伤害/秒。"

LDC: "The effective armor value can not go below %s of its original value, even if it's stripped away entirely, and damage reduction from armor can not exceed %s."
LDC_96CN: "即使装甲完全破坏，伤害减免也不能低于初始值的 %s, 也不能超过 %s"
RAW_96CN: com/fs/starfarer/coreui/refit/Object$8.createImpl - String - "即使装甲完全破坏，伤害减免也不能低于初始值的 %s, 也不能超过 %s"

LDC: "Each capacitor costs %s ordnance point and increases flux capacity by %s."
LDC_96CN: "每提高 %s 点幅能寄存器，就额外获得 %s 点幅能容量。"
RAW_96CN: com/fs/starfarer/coreui/refit/Object$5.createImpl - String - "每提高 %s 点幅能寄存器，就额外获得 %s 点幅能容量。"

LDC: "The maximum speed of this ship under normal combat conditions."
LDC_96CN: "该舰在正常情况下的最高航速。"
RAW_96CN: com/fs/starfarer/coreui/refit/Object$6.createImpl - String - "该舰在正常情况下的最高航速。"

LDC: "When a ship's flux is at zero and it's not generating any flux, it receives a bonus of %s to top speed, as well as a boost to turn rate and acceleration."
LDC_96CN: "当幅能为零时，该舰将获得 %s 点航速的奖励，其机动性也会提高。"
RAW_96CN: com/fs/starfarer/coreui/refit/Object$6.createImpl - String - "当幅能为零时，该舰将获得 %s 点航速的奖励，其机动性也会提高。"

LDC: "Firing most weapons (except, generally, missiles) generates flux."
LDC_96CN: "发射大多数武器 (一般来说，导弹除外) 均会产生软幅能。"
RAW_96CN: com/fs/starfarer/coreui/refit/Object$9.createImpl - String - "发射大多数武器 (一般来说，导弹除外) 均会产生软幅能。"

LDC: "This is the total flux per second that continuously firing all the weapons on the ship will generate."
LDC_96CN: "代表该舰所有武器持续开火时所产生的总幅能量。"
RAW_96CN: com/fs/starfarer/coreui/refit/Object$9.createImpl - String - "代表该舰所有武器持续开火时所产生的总幅能量。"

LDC: "Some weapons can fire more and build up more flux over the short term. This value reflects the sustained flux generation that accounts for the rate at which weapons recharge."
LDC_96CN: "一些武器可以在短期内快速开火，并积累更多幅能。而该值则 与武器 最低幅能输出 / 秒 所挂钩，同时它也代表武器重装时间的长短。"
RAW_96CN: com/fs/starfarer/coreui/refit/Object$9.createImpl - String - "一些武器可以在短期内快速开火，并积累更多幅能。而该值则 与武器 最低幅能输出 / 秒 所挂钩，同时它也代表武器重装时间的长短。"

LDC: "Welcome to the advanced combat tutorial. Let's get started!"
LDC_96CN: "欢迎来到高级作战教程。让我们开始吧！"
RAW_96CN: com/fs/starfarer/tutorial/new.createScript - String - "欢迎来到高级作战教程。让我们开始吧！"

LDC: "Your flagship is still the same Hammerhead, but the point defense lasers have been swapped out for Ion Cannons - more on those later."
LDC_96CN: "您的旗舰仍是艘锤头-级，但 PD 激光替换成离子炮 - 不过这些之后才会提到。"
RAW_96CN: com/fs/starfarer/tutorial/new.createScript - String - "您的旗舰仍是艘锤头-级，但 PD 激光替换成离子炮 - 不过这些之后才会提到。"

LDC: "We've already gone over the basics of using weapons in the previous tutorial. Now, let's take a look at picking the right weapon for the job."
LDC_96CN: "前面我们差不多完成了基本的武器使用教程，现在，让我们看看该如何挑选合适的武器进行攻击。"
RAW_96CN: com/fs/starfarer/tutorial/new.createScript - String - "前面我们差不多完成了基本的武器使用教程，现在，让我们看看该如何挑选合适的武器进行攻击。"

LDC: "Since the enemy ship has its shields up, let's start off by firing some Sabot missiles at it - they are extremely effective at bringing down shields."
LDC_96CN: "因敌舰开启了护盾，所以发射些赛博 SRM 导弹来使其关闭 - 它们对护盾非常有效。"
RAW_96CN: com/fs/starfarer/tutorial/new.createScript - String - "因敌舰开启了护盾，所以发射些赛博 SRM 导弹来使其关闭 - 它们对护盾非常有效。"

LDC: "Fire enough Sabots at the enemy ship to overload its shields."
LDC_96CN: "按 2 键切换武器并发射足够数量的赛博 SRM 使敌舰的护盾过载。"
RAW_96CN: com/fs/starfarer/tutorial/new.createScript - String - "按 2 键切换武器并发射足够数量的赛博 SRM 使敌舰的护盾过载。"

LDC: "Great work! With the shields down and an overload in progress, the enemy ship is vulnerable. The next step is to bring down its armor."
LDC_96CN: "真棒！当敌舰过载时护盾会关闭，并暴露弱点，下一步我们将摧毁他的装甲。"
RAW_96CN: com/fs/starfarer/tutorial/new.createScript - String - "真棒！当敌舰过载时护盾会关闭，并暴露弱点，下一步我们将摧毁他的装甲。"

LDC: "High explosive damage deals 200% to armor, but only 50% to shields."
LDC_96CN: "高爆伤害 能对装甲造成 200% 的伤害，但对护盾却只能造成 50% 的伤害。"
RAW_96CN: com/fs/starfarer/tutorial/new.createScript - String - "高爆伤害 能对装甲造成 200% 的伤害，但对护盾却只能造成 50% 的伤害。"

LDC: "Switch to your Assault Chainguns and punch through the armor. To break through faster, focus your fire on one spot."
LDC_96CN: "切换至突击链炮来打穿装甲，为了能更快的打破装甲，请将火力集中在一点之上。"
RAW_96CN: com/fs/starfarer/tutorial/new.createScript - String - "切换至突击链炮来打穿装甲，为了能更快的打破装甲，请将火力集中在一点之上。"

LDC: "Excellent, the enemy ship is taking hull damage now. Let's finish it off!"
LDC_96CN: "非常好，现在敌舰的结构正受到伤害。让我们来了结他吧！"
RAW_96CN: com/fs/starfarer/tutorial/new.createScript - String - "非常好，现在敌舰的结构正受到伤害。让我们来了结他吧！"

LDC: "Be careful - when a ship is disabled, the explosion deals damage to all nearby ships, except for fighters."
LDC_96CN: "小心 - 当舰船停机，爆炸将对附近所有的舰船造成伤害，战机除外。"
RAW_96CN: com/fs/starfarer/tutorial/new.createScript - String - "小心 - 当舰船停机，爆炸将对附近所有的舰船造成伤害，战机除外。"

LDC: "Make sure you're far enough away to avoid damage. About a ship's length should be enough."
LDC_96CN: "确定您离得足够远来规避伤害，大概保持足够一艘船的距离。"
RAW_96CN: com/fs/starfarer/tutorial/new.createScript - String - "确定您离得足够远来规避伤害，大概保持足够一艘船的距离。"

LDC: "Fragmentation damage deals only 25% to armor and shields, but usually costs little flux and has a high base DPS value, making it effective vs exposed hull, or lightly armored, unshielded targets - like missiles and fighters."
LDC_96CN: "破片伤害 只对装甲和护盾造成 25% 的伤害，但幅能产出很少且基础伤害很高，因此能有效对抗没有装甲保护的结构、轻型装甲，没有护盾的目标 - 如导弹和战机。"
RAW_96CN: com/fs/starfarer/tutorial/new.createScript - String - "破片伤害 只对装甲和护盾造成 25% 的伤害，但幅能产出很少且基础伤害很高，因此能有效对抗没有装甲保护的结构、轻型装甲，没有护盾的目标 - 如导弹和战机。"

LDC: "Energy damage deals 100% of its listed damage to everything."
LDC_96CN: "能量伤害 能对任何目标造成 100% 的伤害。"
RAW_96CN: com/fs/starfarer/tutorial/new.createScript - String - "能量伤害 能对任何目标造成 100% 的伤害。"

LDC: "Some weapons also deal EMP damage in addition to their normal damage type."
LDC_96CN: "而一些武器也同样会在它们的基础伤害之外造成额外的 EMP 伤害。"
RAW_96CN: com/fs/starfarer/tutorial/new.createScript - String - "而一些武器也同样会在它们的基础伤害之外造成额外的 EMP 伤害。"

LDC: "EMP damage does not affect shields, armor, or hull - but it can quickly disable enemy weapons and engines."
LDC_96CN: "EMP 伤害难以威胁到护盾、装甲、结构 - 但它能迅速瘫痪敌舰武器和引擎。"
RAW_96CN: com/fs/starfarer/tutorial/new.createScript - String - "EMP 伤害难以威胁到护盾、装甲、结构 - 但它能迅速瘫痪敌舰武器和引擎。"

LDC: "Your Ion Cannons deal lots of EMP damage (and little else). Switch to the Ion Cannons and disable some of the weapons on the Enforcer."
LDC_96CN: "你的离子炮可以造成大量的 EMP 伤害 (和一点点其他的伤害) 切换到离子炮攻击执法者-级来瘫痪它的武器。"
RAW_96CN: com/fs/starfarer/tutorial/new.createScript - String - "你的离子炮可以造成大量的 EMP 伤害 (和一点点其他的伤害) 切换到离子炮攻击执法者-级来瘫痪它的武器。"

LDC: "Excellent. Now, maneuver behind the enemy ship to disable its engines. You'll need to take out more than half to cause a total flameout."
LDC_96CN: "很好！现在航行其身后去瘫痪它的引擎。您需瘫痪一半以上的引擎来导致其熄火。"
RAW_96CN: com/fs/starfarer/tutorial/new.createScript - String - "很好！现在航行其身后去瘫痪它的引擎。您需瘫痪一半以上的引擎来导致其熄火。"

LDC: "That ship is now a sitting duck - it won't be able to maneuver at all until the engines are back online."
LDC_96CN: "敌舰现在无法动弹了 - 他将无法移动直到他的引擎重新恢复工作。"
RAW_96CN: com/fs/starfarer/tutorial/new.createScript - String - "敌舰现在无法动弹了 - 他将无法移动直到他的引擎重新恢复工作。"

LDC: "Non-EMP weapons can also disable engines and weapons, but EMP weapons bypass armor and get the job done faster."
LDC_96CN: "非 EMP 伤害的武器也能使引擎和武器失效，但 EMP 能绕过装甲更快完成任务。"
RAW_96CN: com/fs/starfarer/tutorial/new.createScript - String - "非 EMP 伤害的武器也能使引擎和武器失效，但 EMP 能绕过装甲更快完成任务。"

LDC: "Let's take another look at shields. Turn on your shields and sit tight for a moment - you'll be attacked with beam weapons."
LDC_96CN: "让我们看看另一种情况，现在打开护盾稍等片刻 - 您将受到光束武器的攻击。"
RAW_96CN: com/fs/starfarer/tutorial/new.createScript - String - "让我们看看另一种情况，现在打开护盾稍等片刻 - 您将受到光束武器的攻击。"

LDC: "As you can see, your ship is not building up flux despite the shields being under fire."
LDC_96CN: "如您所见，火力作用于护盾上并没有造成幅能上涨。"
RAW_96CN: com/fs/starfarer/tutorial/new.createScript - String - "如您所见，火力作用于护盾上并没有造成幅能上涨。"

LDC: "This is because beam weapons generate soft flux when hitting shields."
LDC_96CN: "这是因为光束武器只会对护盾输出软幅能。"
RAW_96CN: com/fs/starfarer/tutorial/new.createScript - String - "这是因为光束武器只会对护盾输出软幅能。"

LDC: "This may make them seem weak - but remember that this flux still needs to be dissipated, leaving that much less flux dissipation to power weapons. Beam weapons are also very efficient and need little flux to fire."
